casebody.data:
RETAINED REALTY, INC.
v.
Eileen M. LENAHAN et al. Supreme Court of Connecticut. Decided February 1, 2017

Eileen M. Lenahan, self-represented, in support of the petition.

Taryn D. Martin and Robert A. Zeigler, in opposition.

The named defendant's petition for certification for appeal from the Appellate Court, 169 Conn. App. 902, 150 A.3d 273 (2016), is denied.
